  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the middle of your head, with that hand shear, they cut approximately, whatever it is, a width around two inches, a stripe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But once a month was stripe down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the basic idea was that they figured if you are such a genius and with your striped suit you can escape-- and most of the people with the tattoo on the arm, at least on your head if you take off your hat, or whatever it is, it's quite obvious that you are a concentration-- and they called it a [NON-ENGLISH] prisoner.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, our work was, there, not only hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But an awful lot of people fell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We started off to be 28,000 at the Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with a minimum of food and a tremendous amount of work, and difficulty of the temperature and the rest of it, what was hard work, real hard work, one day, while we are marching for our famous lunch, I notice that the SS is feeding the German shepherds with potato peels.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that smell and the fume came up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was just an unbelievable temptation, let's call it that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, you're hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I broke line.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I jumped into the place where the shepherds were feeding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I took away a dish of potato peels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was hollering and screaming at me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, that-- the desperation came to the point of what can happen?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They can kill me or I have potato peels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So maybe I'm-- maybe I'm going to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had, probably, stuffed my mouth with an awful lot of potato peels.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
